OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHijab row: Karnataka high  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcourt upholds ban in       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschools and colleges       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A high court in India has ruled that   
OL,6, the hijab is not "essential" to Islam, 
OL,7, paving the way for schools to disallow 
OL,8, headscarves from campuses.             
OL,10,FThe much-awaited verdict comes in the  
OL,11,Fwake of a row over the headscarf in the
OL,12,Fsouthern state of Karnataka.           
OL,14,FA state college's decision in January  
OL,15,Fto bar entry to Muslim girls wearing   
OL,16,Fthe hijab had sparked protests.        
OL,18,FThe issue snowballed, forcing the state
OL,19,Fto shut high schools and colleges for  
OL,20,Fseveral days.                          
